snippet.title: Paleophage - Official Trailer | The Indie Horror Showcase 2023
snippet.description: PALEOPHAGE is a third-person dinosaur survival horror game set in an urban resort. Fight or attempt to outrun over ten varieties of prehistoric creature, solve puzzles and uncover the secrets of the Paleophage, a prehistoric biological nightmare capable of reconstituting ancient life. Coming to PC.
